com.ubudu.iot.dongle

Class Dongle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ubudu.iot.ble.BleDevice
      • com.ubudu.iot.dongle.Dongle

  • public class Dongle
extends BleDevice
    Created by julien on 4/26/17.

    Class representing an Ubudu dongle. Ubudu dongle is a Bluetooth LE device that is discoverable and supports two way communication. Ubudu dongle exposes one service of UUID and two characteristics: one read-only and one write-only.
